1. Find a number is Odd or Even using Ternary and Arithmetic Operators
public class question1 {
public static void main(String[] args) {
		//ternary operator
		int num1=6;
		String	ans =(num1%2==0)? "Even":"Odd";
		System.out.println(ans);
		
		}

}

2. Write program using Logical Operators

  public class question2{
